The objective of our bartending school is to give you the skills, and confidence required to begin bartending the day you finish our school. We feature a two part bartending training course. Part one of the bartending course is designed to give you hands on training behind a real bar. This phase of the bartending school will give you the skills necessary to begin bartending immediately after finishing the bartending course. The second part of our bartending program is assisting you in finding a bartending job. You learn bartending by working behind a real bar, giving you the bartending skills and confidence to begin bartending
